@startuml commit-group-strategies
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title dev-workgraph — **Extending commit-group strategies**\nPluggable partition · fixed runner · same GroupRecord for report

legend top left
  |= Layer |= Customizable? |
  | **Strategy** | **Yes** — partition only |
  | **commit-group action** | **No** — buildGroupRecord + LLM classify/compose |
  | **report** | **No** — reads groups/*.json |
endlegend

rectangle "src/lib/commit-group/" #E8F5E9 {
  card "**CommitGroupStrategy**\nid · displayName\ncliOptions · pickCliOptions\ninit · partition · formatSummary" as IFACE

  card "**registry.ts**\nCOMMIT_GROUP_STRATEGIES\n(sole import of concrete strategies)" as REG #C8E6C9

  card "**day-gap-strategy.ts** (default)\n--days · --max-commits\ngroupByGap · extensionSessions\nfileKey = timestampEnd" as DAY #FFF8E1

  card "**your-strategy.ts** (e.g. jira)\nown CLI flags\npartition by ticket\nfileKey = PROJ-123" as CUSTOM #E3F2FD

  card "cli-options.ts\nregisterCommitGroupStrategyOptions" as CLI #FAFAFA
}

rectangle "src/actions/commit-group.ts (runner)" #FFF3E0 {
  card "load commits + filter empty" as LOAD
  card "buildGroupRecord (D)" as BUILD
  card "classify + compose (M:c)" as LLM
  card "groups/<fileKey>.json" as OUT
}

REG --> DAY : wires
REG ..> CUSTOM : append here
IFACE .. DAY : implements
IFACE .. CUSTOM : implements

CLI --> REG : registers cliOptions

LOAD --> IFACE : init then partition
IFACE --> BUILD : buckets
BUILD --> LLM
LLM --> OUT

note bottom of REG
  **run** resolves strategy:
  1 registered = silent default
  N registered = picker or saved
  **commitGroupStrategy** in repo config
end note

note bottom of OUT
  **GroupRecord** schema unchanged.
  report folds groups regardless of
  how buckets were formed.
end note

@enduml


@startuml commit-group-strategies-flow
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #888888

title **commit-group** — strategy vs runner responsibilities

|Strategy (plugin)|
start
:Read strategyCli from CLI\npickCliOptions;
:init(ctx) — prompts, persist\n(e.g. groupThresholdDays);
:partition(commits) to buckets;
note right
  Each bucket:
  members[] + fileKey
end note
stop

|Runner (fixed)|
start
:loadCommitRecords + filter empty;
:getCommitGroupStrategy(--strategy);
:await strategy.init + partition;
:resolve commitModel;
partition "foreach bucket" {
  :buildGroupRecord(members);
  if (group file has model?) then (yes)
    :skip;
  else (no)
    :(M:c) classify + compose;
    :write GroupRecord;
  endif
}
stop

@enduml
